		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm just glad i asked!<br /><br />The shots of the open NES in that Solstice video are interesting, they seemed to have plugged in some sort of board directly connected to a computer. They also have their own music composer utility, perhaps that was just run on the NES as well. Very cool stuff!<br /><br />I also ran across this somewhere: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HP_64000">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HP_64000</a><!-- m -->, basically a computer with a built in emulator for various CPUs.

		

