		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />That depends on what machines the <a href="http://patpend.net/articles/ar/sil10.html" class="postlink">Mirage emulator</a> ran on. Silhouette, a consumer-oriented fork from Mirage and one of the first publicly available Super NES emulators, ran on Macs.

		

		</td>
